# Form Standards

## Structure
- Use React Hook Form
- Implement Zod validation schemas
- Type all form fields
- Include proper labels and ARIA
- Support keyboard navigation

## Validation
- Client-side validation
- Server-side validation
- File size limits (20MB max)
- Audio length limits (5 min max)
- Supported format validation

## Error States
- Field-level errors
- Form-level errors
- Network errors
- Validation errors
- Upload errors

## User Experience
- Loading states
- Success feedback
- Error messages
- Progress indicators
- Clear reset functionality

## Accessibility
- Proper HTML5 input types
- Error announcements
- Required field marking
- Focus management
- Screen reader support 